original_title: Hot Wheels Acceleracers: Episode 3 Swamp Attack
overview: In episode 3, "Swamp Attack," the Teku and Metal Maniacs compete in a dense swamp racing realm. The racers soon realize they must put aside their differences and work as a team to battle the mutant swamp creatures and the Drones in their jed-enhanced vehicles. With the lucky discovery of a couple HyperPod vehicles and some serious driving, the racers get a shot at their first Accele-Charger car enhancer.
title: Hot Wheels Acceleracers: Episode 3 Swamp Attack
